# hit_distribution_dp.ts — Math Lockdown

Do NOT modify the mathematical formulas or logic in this file without a formal peer-review/approval step.

Protected:
- binom(n,k) and binomPmf(k, n, p): P(X=k) = C(n,k) p^k (1-p)^{n-k}.
- computeHitDistributionDP: recurrence next[j] += dp[j]*(1-p), next[j+1] += dp[j]*p.
- computePrizePicksHitDistributionIid: same binomial PMF with avgProb.

Allowed without approval: comments, types. No changes to equations or recurrence.
